==English==

===Etymology===

Compare with French [[agressif]].

===Pronunciation===
IPA: [[WEAE]] /ʌˈgɹɛs.ɪv/

===Adjective===
'''aggressive'''

#Tending or disposed to aggress; characterized by aggression; making assaults; unjustly attacking; as, an aggressive  policy, war, person, nation.

